import React from 'react';
import { 
    SidebarContainer, 
    Icon, 
    CloseIcon,
    SidebarWrapper,
    SidebarMenu,
    SidebarLink,
    SideBtnWrap,
    SidebarRoute
} from './SidebarElements';

const Sidebar = ({isOpen, toggle}) => {
    return (
        <>
            <SidebarContainer isOpen={isOpen} onClick={toggle}>
                <Icon onClick={toggle}>
                    <CloseIcon />
                </Icon>
                <SidebarWrapper>
                    <SidebarMenu>
                        <SidebarLink onClick={toggle} to="about">
                            About
                        </SidebarLink>
                        <SidebarLink onClick={toggle} to="discover">
                            Discover
                        </SidebarLink>
                        <SidebarLink onClick={toggle} to="services">
                            Services
                        </SidebarLink>
                        <SidebarLink onClick={toggle} to="signup">
                            Sign up
                        </SidebarLink>
                    </SidebarMenu>
                    <SideBtnWrap>
                        <SidebarRoute to="/signin">
                            Sign In
                        </SidebarRoute>
                    </SideBtnWrap>
                </SidebarWrapper>
            </SidebarContainer>
        </>
    )
}

export default Sidebar
